rComments: Makes tests super hard and only does the easy questions in class.

Very approachable guy, lectures provide challenging material but I always feel like I understand the material better afterwards. Accessible outside of class and friendly in class, knows many students' names and makes jokes with us. One of my favourite profs, would definitely recommend.

Professor Huan Vo is a really responsible teacher. He's also very amiable and know almost half of the class' name. He also gives detailed and logical lecture for the exercise in class, which really help us a lot.

He gives very detailed lectures and provides enough examples to help you understand all the tough parts. Furthermore, he is a very accessible friend after class and always make jokes with his students.
